{[#]Black played} 16... Ba6 {yielding him a solid but somewhat passive
position and eventually lost.} ({He trained from} 16... cxb4 {in view of the
familiar} 17. Na2 {Was he right in doing so? ***No he was not!} Nxd5 $3 {
