{[#]Do you share my feeling that White is hanging a bit?!} 17... Nxg3 $1 {
Right!} 18. Nxb5 ({If} 18. fxg3 Bxc3 19. Bxc3 Qe3+ 20. Kh2 Qxc3 $17 {simply
wins a pawn.}) 18... Rxb5 19. fxg3 cxb4 (19... Ba6 $17 {might have been even
