Nce4 Nh5 {allows White deviating from the similar line below with} 11. Bg5 f6
12. Bh4 g5 13. e3 Ng7 14. Qf3 Be7 15. Bg3 f5 16. Nxc5 g4 17. Qf4 dxc5 18. Qe5
Kf8 19. d6 Bf6 20. Qd5 Ra7 21. Qxc5 Rd7 22. Nc4 $44 {Fauland,A (2390)-Wahls,M 
