b4 11. Nce4 f5 12. g4 $1 {The point behind White's whole opening play.} Nf6 (
12... fxg4 {allwos the enemy knight staying in the centre with strong pressure
after} 13. Nc4) 13. gxf5 Nxe4 14. Nxe4 Bxf5 15. Ng3 (15. Bg5 Be7 16. Bxe7 Qxe7
