13. Bd3 Bf8 $5 $146 14. O-O Nbd7 15. Ne3 Nh5 16. Bg5 f6 17. Bh4 Nf4 $132) 12...
b3 $1 {Using the favourable moment.} 13. Qd3 (13. Qxb3 Nxe4 {favours Black as
